Dana Reeve https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dana_Reeve 0 Dana Charles Reeve (née Morosini; March 17, 1961 – March 6, 2006) was an American actress, singer, and activist for disability causes. She was the wife of actor Christopher Reeve. Dana_Charles_Reeve ( née_Morosini ; March_17_,_1961 – March_6_,_2006 ) was an_American_actress , singer , and activist for disability_causes .
